{"tid":817580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重案組拘興德學校前校長陳章萍 落案起訴行使虛假文書","createTime":"2018-09-13T12:42:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T09:43:30.000Z","uid":44562,"like":176,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"dd9652c0c732ac6b44a2fab8d72121bd910cb647","tid":817580,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:42:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180913/large/1536840997_4ffd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180913%2Flarge%2F1536840997_4ffd.jpg&h=1b3658b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屯門興德學校前校長陳章萍涉行使虛假文書被捕！警方於去年8月接獲相關政策局（據悉是教育局）轉介，指屯門慶平路一學校的校長懷疑向教育局出示虛假的招聘員工面試記錄，屯門警區重案組第一隊人員經調查及徵詢法律意見後，今日於屯門拘捕一名46歲姓陳女子，涉嫌「行使虛假文書」。<br />\n消息稱，被捕人是屯門興德學校前校長陳章萍，她已被警方控以一項「行使虛假文書」罪，案件將於9月20日（下周四）在屯門裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你都有今日喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d5a88c530bd17b1fbeb18362952ff80a291706","tid":817580,"uid":72621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea9bcbc5ab02746c114923617064e295bc0dc1b","tid":817580,"uid":129474,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:43:32.000Z","msg":"入策有無西餅食"},{"pid":"212704313d9bbbfa1023532e3ed2f15c8bbaefb6","tid":817580,"uid":125168,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:44:11.000Z","msg":"條肥婆之前辭職袋好撚多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b587f61cf995be6be5be299fa6e1fd2e175e9e37","tid":817580,